hints.freeDraw: Ssit yerna zuɣer, serreḥ ticki tfukeḍ
hints.text: Tixidest: tzemreḍ daɣen ad ternuḍ aḍris s usiti snat n tikkal anida tebɣiḍ s ufecku n tefrayt
hints.linearElementMulti: Ssit ɣef tenqiḍt taneggarut neɣ ssed taqeffalt Escape neɣ taqeffalt Kcem akken ad tfakkeḍ
hints.lockAngle: Tzemreḍ ad tḥettmeḍ tiɣmert s tuṭṭfa n tqeffalt SHIFT
hints.resize:
Tzemreḍ ad tḥettemeḍ assaɣ s tuṭṭfa n tqeffalt SHIFT mi ara tettbeddileḍ tiddi,
ma teṭṭfeḍ ALT abeddel n tiddi ad yili si tlemmast
hints.rotate: Tzemreḍ ad tḥettemeḍ tiɣemmar s tuṭṭfa n SHIFT di tuzzya
hints.lineEditor_info: Ssit snat n tikkal neɣ ssed taqeffalt Kcem akken ad tẓergeḍ tinqiḍin
hints.lineEditor_pointSelected: Ssed taqeffalt kkes akken ad tekkseḍ tanqiḍt, CtrlOrCmd+D akken ad tsiselgeḍ, neɣ zuɣer akken ad tesmuttiḍ

errorSplash.openIssueMessage_pre: Nḥuder aṭas akken ur nseddu ara talɣut n usayes-inek (m) di tuccḍa. Ma yella asayes-inek (m) mačči d amaẓlay, ttxil-k (m) xemmem ad ḍefreḍ
errorSplash.openIssueMessage_post: Ma ulac uɣilif seddu talɣut ukessar-agi s wenɣal akked usenṭeḍ di GitHub issue.

roomDialog.desc_intro: Tzemreḍ ad d-teɛerḍeḍ medden ɣer usayes-inek (m) amiran akken ad ttekkin yid-k.
roomDialog.desc_privacy: Ur tqelliq ara, tiɣimit tsseqdac awgelhen ixef s ixef, dɣa ayen ara tsunɣeḍ ad iqqim d amaẓlay. Ula d aqeddac-nneɣ ur yezmir ara ad iwali acu txeddemeḍ.
roomDialog.desc_inProgressIntro: Tiɣimit n umɛawen s srid tetteddu akka tura.
roomDialog.desc_shareLink: Bḍu aseɣwen-agi akked medden ukud tebɣiḍ ad temɛawaneḍ:
roomDialog.desc_exitSession: Aḥbas n tɣimit ad k (m) yesenser si texxamt, maca ad tizmireḍ ad tkemmeleḍ amahil s usayes, s wudem adigan. Ẓer belli ayagi ur yettḥaz ara imdanen-nniḍen, yerna ad izmiren ad kemmelen ad mɛawanen di tsuffeɣt-nnsen.
